Preheat the oven to 170C/150C Fan/Gas 3.Mix the cabbage with the rest of the ingredients and put in an ovenproof dish.Season well and cover with foil.Bake for 1–1½ hours, or until the cabbage is tender and juicy. Mix the ingredients together two to three times during cooking.Allow to cool, then store in the fridge. Reheat when needed.